Class Description
AnalysisStrategy
This class perform the real analysis on different analysis strategy type.
AnalysisTypeCreator
This class acts as the Creator on Factory Method Design Pattern.
Calculator
This class acts as the Context in the Strategy Design Pattern.
ConfirmedCasesForMenReader
This class retrieves data from local files, Dataset.csv, which provides data for calculations of ConfirmedCasesForMenStrategy.
ConfirmedCasesForWomenReader
This class retrieves data from local files, Dataset.csv, which provides data for calculations of ConfirmedCasesForWomenStrategy.
ConfirmedCasesReader
This class retrieves data from website which provides data for calculations of ConfirmedCasesStrategy.
CountryListOperation
This class defines an interface for operations on country list (including adding, removing and acquiring list of selected countries).
CountryListOperationImpl
This class implements the interface of handling the operations on country list.
CountryOperationImpl
This class implements the interface of providing the coordination of country passed by parameter.
CovidConfirmCasesCreator
This class acts as the creator of CovidConfirmCasesStrategy object.
CovidConfirmCasesFemalesCreator
This class acts as the creator of the CovidConfirmCasesForWomenStrategy object.
CovidConfirmCasesMalesCreator
This class acts as the creator of the CovidConfirmCasesForMenStrategy object.
CovidConfirmCasesPerCapitaCreator
This class acts as the creator of the CovidConfirmCasesPerCapitaStrategy object.
CovidConfirmCasesPerCapitaStrategy
This class perform the real analysis on the total confirmed Covid-19 cases per capita for a given country or a list of countries
CovidConfirmCasesStrategy
This class perform the real analysis on the total confirmed cases for a given country or a list of countries
CovidConfirmeCasesForMenStrategy
This class perform the real analysis on the the total confirmed Covid-19 cases of males for a given country or a list of countries.
CovidConfirmeCasesForWomenStrategy
This class perform the real analysis on the the total confirmed Covid-19 cases of females for a given country or a list of countries.
DataRetrieve
This class retrieves data from local files or websites, which can be used to proceed the further calculations of analysis.
DispatchJobFacade
A class is responsible for dispatch task based on facade design pattern which is for coordinating activities between the UI and the backend services
ICountryOperation
This class defines an interface for providing the coordination of country
IUserDao
A interface for login the COVID-19 STATS System.
JsonTools
A networking tool to retrieve data from internet and parse it.
KnownCountryFactory
This class is used to acquire the list of known countries, which can be useful when the system needs to check whether the input country name is valid or not.
LoginFrame
The entrance class for COVID-19 STATS System.
MainFrame
This class constructs the dashboard of COVID-19 STATS SYSTEM.
MapPanel
A customized JPanel help to render background image and red filled circle.
MessageObservable
A class implement Observable interface mainly function as a observer collector.
Observable
A interface define the basic function for observable design pattern.
Observer
A class can implement the Observer interface when it ants to be informed of changes in observable objects.
PathTools
A class used to generate the path of working directory.
PopulationReader
This class retrieves data from local files, country-by-population.json, which provides population of countries
Reader
This class gets the data from DataRetrieve class, such that clients can directly calls this Reader class to get whatever data they need for the analysis calculation.
ReaderImpl
This class implements the Reader class, used to set and get the data needed for analysis calculations.
ResponseResult
A class functions as common response result including response code and message attribute.
ResultTextArea
A customized class used to display analysis result.
SelectedCountryList
This class is used to show the country list which has been selected by users, and has been checked for the existence in known country list.
User
A class used to store user information.
UserDaoImpl
A class implements IUserDao interface.
UserDaoProxy
A proxy class which implements IUserDao interface is to make program more flexible.
WarningDialog
A customized class to display dialog.
